headline: Ookla Research Shows that Xfinity Mobile Speeds Have Skyrocketed 150 Percent
summary: PHILADELPHIA - Ookla's latest Speedtest Intelligence research credits Xfinity Mobile's PowerBoost for delivering customers 150 percent faster speeds since the innovative feature launched in 2024....
